title: Christmas Wish #12: The O'Brien Family
description: Kat nominated her friend Sharon who was dealing with some health issues in the hospital so she wasn't home for a few days when there was a pipe leak and her house was flooded.  She lost everything and this was the house her dad built and she grew up in.
